  <li class="comment-item" data-cid="393997753">
    <div class="comment">
      <h3>
        <span class="comment-vote">
            <span id="c-393997753" class="vote-count">379</span>
              <a id="btn-393997753" href="" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="393997753">有用</a>

        </span>
        <span class="comment-info">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/shermmm/">夏尔米米米</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/393997753">2012-06-17 03:37:00</a>
          <span class="comment-location"></span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">杂文不好写，写着写着就沦为了平庸或是偏激。小波的情绪虽然激荡不止，却依旧能不动声色的娓娓道来。他的文章论辩性虽强，却也能让人禁不住发笑。不是每一篇都精彩，也不是每一个事例都别致，但是，这股揭示真理的认真劲儿就足以让我产生共鸣。当然，几近引起不寒而栗的更强烈的共鸣还是在于，我和他全部观点的不谋而合。</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/1014578/?comment_id=393997753"></div>
    </div>
